text: Nargiz Pashayeva (; born 12 May 1987) is an Azerbaijani former footballer who played as a forward. She has been a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers
